  "title": "People from different neighborhoods in Curitiba report the same round orange UFO [2000]*",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/15/people-from-different-neighborhoods-in-curitiba-report-the-same-round-orange-ufo-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-u1",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">*Interrelated case: [<a href=\"https://brazilianufoarchives.wordpress.com/2020/06/15/a-round-orange-ufo-hovered-over-curitiba-2000/\">see case ARX.0.0.570 &#8220;A round orange UFO hovered over Curitiba [2000]</a>&#8220;*</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 13th, 2000</strong>. Time: 00h20 am. Duration: 1 hour. This report of the sighting of a round orange UFO in the Pilarzinho neighborhood was not the only one in Curitiba on the same night and in the same time frame [<a href=\"https://brazilianufoarchives.wordpress.com/2020/06/15/a-round-orange-ufo-hovered-over-curitiba-2000/\">see case ARX.0.0.570 &#8220;A round orange UFO hovered over Curitiba [2000]</a>&#8220;. In Pilarzinho, just like in Xaxim neighborhood, the witness reported the sighting of an unidentified round flying object, orange-colored moving northwards. The witness informed that the weather in that particular night. The sky was partly cloudy.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.569. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Avistamento de ovni em Pilarzinho, Curitiba, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
